quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,79,"Àlàáfíà kí ó máa bá (Ànábì) Nūh láààrin gbogbo ẹ̀dá."
  37,80,"Dájúdájú báyẹn ni Àwa ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)."
  37,81,"Dájúdájú ó wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  38,58,"Oríṣiríṣi (ìyà) mìíràn bí irú rẹ̀ (tún wà fún wọn)."
  38,59,"Èyí ni ìjọ kan tó máa wọ inú Iná pẹ̀lú yín. (Àwọn aṣíwájú nínú Iná sì máa wí pé:) “Kò sí máawolẹ̀-máarọra fún wọn.” Dájúdájú wọn yóò wọ inú Iná ni."
  38,60,"(Àwọn ọmọlẹ́yìn nínú Iná) máa wí pé: “Rárá, ẹ̀yin náà kò sí máawolẹ̀-máarọra fún yín. Ẹ̀yin l’ẹ pè wá síbi èyí (tó bí Iná).” Ó sì burú ní ibùgbé."
  39,43,"Tàbí wọ́n mú àwọn olùṣìpẹ̀ mìíràn lẹ́yìn Allāhu ni? Sọ pé: “(Wọ́n mú wọn ní olùṣìpẹ̀) tó sì jẹ́ pé wọn kò ní agbára kan kan, wọn kò sì níí làákàyè!”"
  39,44,"Sọ pé: “Ti Allāhu ni gbogbo ìṣìpẹ̀ pátápátá. TiRẹ̀ ni ìjọba àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Lẹ́yìn náà, ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ ni wọn yóò da yín padà sí.”"
  39,45,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá dárúkọ Allāhu nìkan ṣoṣo, ọkàn àwọn tí kò gbàgbọ́ nínú Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn máa sá kúrò (níbi mímú Allāhu ní ọ̀kan ṣoṣo). Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sì dárúkọ àwọn mìíràn (tí wọ́n ń jọ́sìn fún) lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀, nígbà náà ni wọn yóò máa dunnú."
  40,22,"Ìyẹn nítorí pé, àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ wọn ń wá bá wọn pẹ̀lú àwọn ẹ̀rí tó yanjú, ṣùgbọ́n wọ́n ṣàì gbàgbọ́. Nítorí náà, Allāhu mú wọn. Dájúdájú Òun ni Alágbára, Ẹni líle níbi ìyà."
  40,23,"Dájúdájú A fi àwọn àmì Wa àti ẹ̀rí tó yanjú rán (Ànábì) Mūsā níṣẹ́"
  40,24,"sí Fir‘aon àti Hāmọ̄n àti Ƙọ̄rūn. Ṣùgbọ́n wọ́n wí pé: “Òpìdán, òpùrọ́ ni (Ànábì Mūsā).”"
  41,1,"Hā mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1.]
  41,2,"Ìmísí kan (nìyí) tó sọ̀kalẹ̀ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Àjọkẹ́-ayé, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  41,3,"Tírà kan ni tí wọ́n ṣàlàyé àwọn āyah inú rẹ̀,(ó ń jẹ́) al-Ƙur’ān (tí wọ́n sọ̀kalẹ̀ ní) èdè Lárúbáwá fún ìjọ tó nímọ̀. {1}",footnotes:1:[Ìtúmọ̀ mìíràn “Tírà kan ni tí wọ́n pín àwọn āyah inú rẹ̀ sínú àwọn sūrah.” (Tafsīr at-Tashīl li ‘ulūmi-ttanzīl libn Juziy).]
